Subject: [PATCH] v1.0.0: Initial Release - Interactive Wayru Network Timeline

This is the first official release of WayruCo, featuring:

- Interactive timeline with 21 verified milestones (March 2021 - December 2025)
- Cybernetic visualization with animated ship tracking
- Scroll-based navigation with 9 seconds per milestone
- Clickable milestone cards with verified proof links
- Founder profiles visible at Team Formation milestone
- Audio feedback system with toggle control
- Visual progress bars on each milestone
- Responsive full-screen design
- Comprehensive documentation and contribution guidelines
- Mission and vision statements for open internet initiative

